751
00:33:39,500 --> 00:33:40,860
What a difficult time.

752
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:44,360
The people didn't wanna hear him.

753
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:47,420
The people resisted his message.

754
00:33:47,420 --> 00:33:49,760
The people wanted to kill him.

755
00:33:49,760 --> 00:33:50,840
Amen?

756
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:52,240
I mean, they imprisoned him.

757
00:33:52,240 --> 00:33:54,760
I mean, all the things that happened to Jeremiah,

758
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:56,740
and we find all of this that would happen,

759
00:33:56,740 --> 00:34:00,900
and Jeremiah's ministering at this very difficult time.

