00:50:03,580 --> 00:50:05,140
she'll take a Bible and show you.

997
00:50:05,140 --> 00:50:07,420
I can know for sure that heaven is your home.

998
00:50:07,420 --> 00:50:08,500
If you're saved this morning,

999
00:50:08,500 --> 00:50:10,500
maybe you just need to come and thank God for His presence.

1000
00:50:10,500 --> 00:50:14,660
Maybe you've been living under the circumstances.

1001
00:50:14,660 --> 00:50:16,820
You've been dealing with some of that anxiety, fear,

1002
00:50:16,820 --> 00:50:18,300
worry, so on and so forth,

1003
00:50:18,300 --> 00:50:21,940
and you just need to come and thank God for the reminder.

1004
00:50:21,940 --> 00:50:23,480
Not that you forgot that He was with you,

1005
00:50:23,480 --> 00:50:25,500
but just the reminder that you'd rejoice

1006
00:50:25,500 --> 00:50:28,700
and thank Him for it and live each day

1007
00:50:28,740 --> 00:50:30,860
with the awareness that God is with you.

1008
00:50:30,860 --> 00:50:33,080
As Kimberly plays, the altar is open.

